headline.print_headline: VW CFO Sees Emerging Markets Turmoil Hitting Auto Markets
headline.main: VW CFO Sees Emerging Markets Turmoil Hitting Auto Markets

lead_paragraph: Volkswagen's finance chief said on Friday the German carmaker expected economic turmoil in emerging countries to decrease demand for cars, one reason the company's 2014 outlook was cautious.
